{"tid":702482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫襯美國] 中印擬組採購聯盟 擴大進口美國原油","createTime":"2018-06-15T02:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T02:06:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2efd970745a05569c728aefd50728d3d6891032","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"中印擬組採購聯盟 擴大進口美國原油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3199690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3199690&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b3ce901a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3199690</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博資訊報導，亞洲兩大石油買家─中國與印度正在討論擴大進口美國原油，並可能組成採購聯盟，以對抗石油輸出國組織（OPEC）對國際油市的操控，使油價不致失控。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">印度官員表示，此原油採購聯盟可能先由印度與中國組成，南韓、日本及其他主要買主將後續加入。儘管OPEC仍主導亞洲原油供應，但亞洲所有主要原油進口國幾乎都積極轉向美國原油。</span><br />\n<br />\n印度石油部長普拉漢5月時指出，他已向沙烏地阿拉伯能源部長法利赫關切油價上漲；中國各大煉油業者近月來也減少採購沙國原油，表示油價太貴。<br />\n<br />\n中國石油天然氣集團11日指出，該公司董事長王宜林與印度石油公司董事長在北京會面，討論加強石油與天然氣業務合作。<br />\n<br />\n印度官員表示，中、印兩大買主若能合作，對OPEC將是一大挑戰，使OPEC進一步面臨墨西哥灣及德州頁岩石油的競爭。"},{"pid":"c111b435da6499273558fb3e23450b5dba3dbf81","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"挑戰OPEC？ 中印擬與日韓組「美國石油購買聯盟」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2458267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2458267&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b9724f1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2458267&h=feadd3b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2458267</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕傳中國和印度正討論組建聯盟，購買更多美國石油，以減少對石油輸出國組織（OPEC）產油國的依賴。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》今（14）報導，印度政府官員13日透露，印度和中國希望少對OPEC國家石油的依賴，正考慮共同提高美國石油的進口量，藉此向OPEC國施加壓力，抑制油價上漲。印度官員表示，除了中國，也考慮拉攏日本、南韓加入美國石油購買聯盟。中國、南韓尚未回應此消息，日本經濟產業省石油和天然氣部主任Masato Sasaki，對此表示並不知情。<br />\n<br />\nInterfax Global Energy分析師庫馬（Abhishek Kumar）指出，若石油供應來源多樣化，中國和印度將受益於石油生產商間的競爭，對這兩個能源消耗大國而言，能以最便宜的價格購買石油非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》指出，OPEC國面臨的挑戰不少，雖然OPEC仍然是亞洲的主要石油供應國，但在美國石油出口的40年禁令於2015年解除後，幾乎所有亞洲大型進口商都漸趨轉向進口美國石油；OPEC內部，沙烏地阿拉伯認為去年實施的減產措施，已縮小石油供應過剩狀況，因此支持增產，但伊朗、伊拉克和委內瑞拉則反對提高產量。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》寫到，若中、印合作抵制OPEC石油，將威脅OPEC在亞洲石油市場的統治地位。"},{"pid":"d9e3133c1f0e8b710bc241efd8f51e29a9c0d9df","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"美二疊紀盆地產油量 估10年後超越多數OPEC國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2458630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2458630&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c46738dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2458630&h=300b2669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2458630</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕<span style=\"color: red;\">知名英國經濟預測及商業諮詢機構馬基特（IHS Markit）估計，美國德州二疊紀盆地的石油產量，至2023年將增長2倍，達540萬桶，超越除了沙烏地阿拉伯以外的OPEC國。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，英國經濟預測及商業諮詢機構馬基特13日指出，美國二疊紀盆地的石油產量在過去2年快速增長，估計美國二疊紀盆地的石油產量，在2023年將增至2倍，達到540萬桶，超越除了沙烏地阿拉伯以外的OPEC國。二疊紀盆地石油產量，也將佔2023年的全球石油生產增長量的60%，馬基特預計，屆時西德州原油價格平均將為每桶60美元或更高。<br />\n<br />\n據美國能源情報署（Energy Information Administration），二疊紀盆地5月的石油產量為每日320萬桶，預估6月的產量每日將增加7.8萬桶。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，中國和印度近日則有意組成聯盟，透過購買美國石油，減少對OPEC國石油的依賴。<br />\n<br />\n真&middot;石油大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b4ee509f9f1a2ddaa3246dbe431f53286dad41","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904ac0e003b04d109490701c048bc39f1e244f7f","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc45dad43a838cbcdd2cecc2c2d28f8ed94cb71","tid":702482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfd814fb8a27f86a233dcd2636555f62afca7cf","tid":702482,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"天佑美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1de2803cb228c277cb25b848a58218999e5c96","tid":702482,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"一個美國揮低哂OPEC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備發撚過豬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770ac05a1a825da9021592c9141a0173326040c8","tid":702482,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1de2803cb228c277cb25b848a58218999e5c96","tid":702482,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"一個美國揮低哂OPEC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備發撚過豬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"儲左半個世界既石油  等食哂中東之後就發圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130dd27e29fbbd928ce9621068fec0f9ab2d378f","tid":702482,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770ac05a1a825da9021592c9141a0173326040c8","tid":702482,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1de2803cb228c277cb25b848a58218999e5c96","tid":702482,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"一個美國揮低哂OPEC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備發撚過豬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"儲左半個世界既石油  等食哂中東之後就發圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:06:33.000Z","msg":"真係好堅<br />\n咁忍得?<br />\n<br />\nbtw 油價會唔會升"}]}